description = "Pops the host (Node2D or Control) with a volume-preserving stretch that springs back via a real spring (the stiffness/damping knobs) — bouncier + more organic than the tween Squash & Stretch. Positive = stretch tall (a jump), negative = squash wide (a landing)."
